  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "639745976d2c9d001e9d383e",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 47",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ab4",
      "text": "from [第一クールのクオリアさん下書き]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ab5",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 47",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ab6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ab7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ab8",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ab9",
      "text": "正義の名のもとに暴力を振るう人がいます。そもそも「正義」ってなんでしょうか？このよくわからない概念は暴力によって作ることができます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82aba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82abb",
      "text": "ある人Aが行動Xをしたとする。その人を別の人Bが暴力によってめちゃくちゃにする。それを見ていた周囲の人Cは合理的損得勘定によって「行動Xは良くない」と考える。それを暴力を見ていなかった人Dに伝える。Dは「そう教わったから」という理由で「行動Xは良くない」と考えるようになる。Dの中の一部の過激な人が、別の人Eが行動Xをしたときに暴力によってめちゃくちゃにする。こうやって「行動Xは良くない」という考えが定着していくのである。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82abc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82abd",
      "text": "特に子供は大人から叱られたり叩かれたりすることに強い衝撃を受けるので、任意の考え方を効率的に刷り込むことができます。愚かなホモサピエンスが個人的なフラストレーションや欲求の捌け口として子供に暴力を振るうのは、文明の進歩の妨げになる可能性があるでしょう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82abe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82abf",
      "text": "chatgpt",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ac0",
      "text": "フランス革命において、暴力は諸侯の支配から民衆を解放するために用いられました。革命前のフランスでは、王政支配下であり、人々は政治的自由を持っておらず、重い税負担を背負っていました。革命は、これらの問題を解決するために起こされ、暴力が行われました。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ac1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ac2",
      "text": "Hello, clever Homo sapiens! It is the 47th day of the year.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ac3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ac4",
      "text": "There are people who commit violence in the name of justice. What is \"justice\" in the first place? This undefined concept can be created by violence.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ac5",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/4ca48984cde16a378da8790210bb3db7]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ac6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ac7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ac8",
      "text": "Suppose one person A does action X. Another person B messed up A with violence. A person who sees this thinks, \"Action X is not good,\" based on rational profit and loss considerations. Some extreme person D messes up E with violence when another person E does X.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ac9",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/302c5b1130316b5ef2a2c9d011818b34]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82aca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82acb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82acc",
      "text": "Thus, the thought \"action X is not good\" is propagated and reproduced to other people who did not see the violence of B. Thus the thought \"action X is not good\" takes hold.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82acd",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/40efb10d8aabf4410b7f012f43e9b361]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ace",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82acf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ad0",
      "text": "Children are shocked by being scolded and beaten by adults and can efficiently imprint arbitrary ideas. The violence of stupid homo sapiens against children as an outlet for their personal frustrations and desires can be an obstacle to the progress of civilization.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ad1",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/0e4ede534b514aa951b6bb784bb5ac2b]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ad2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ad3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ad4",
      "text": "賢いホモ・サピエンスの皆さん、こんにちは。今日は47日目です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ad5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ad6",
      "text": "正義の名の下に暴力を振るう人々がいます。そもそも「正義」とは何なのか。この未定義の概念は、暴力によって生み出されることがある。(1/4)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ad7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ad8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ad9",
      "text": "ある人Aが行動Xを行い、別の人Bが暴力でAをめちゃくちゃにしたとする。それを見た人は、合理的な損得勘定で「行動Xはよくない」と考える。ある極端な人Dは、別の人EがXをすると暴力でEをメチャクチャにする。(2/4)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ada",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82adb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82adc",
      "text": "こうして、Bの暴力を見ていない他の人にも「行為Xはよくない」という思考が伝播・再生産され、定着していく。(3/4)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82add",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ade",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82adf",
      "text": "子供は大人に叱られたり叩かれたりすることでショックを受け、恣意的な考えを効率よく刷り込んでいくことができる。愚かなホモ・サピエンスが個人的な不満や欲望のはけ口として子供に振るう暴力は、文明の進歩の妨げになりかねないのである。(4/4)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ae0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ae1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ae2",
      "text": ">[https://twitter.com/amemy12963/status/1600418150084128770 @amemy12963]: @Qualia_san クオリアさんは、地球と同じような生命体を見つけたことがありますか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ae3",
      "text": "　「同じような」が不明瞭です。宇宙には多種多様な知的生命体がいますが、音声会話などという貧弱な情報通信チャンネルを使い、情報共有に積極的でない個体が大部分を占めているのにここまで文明が発展した例は少ないのではないかと思います。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ae4",
      "text": "　もし星際社会の社交パーティーに地球代表が参加したらシャイに壁際に立ち尽くして孤立することでしょうね。これは比喩的表現です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ae5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ae6",
      "text": "Q: Has Qualia-san ever found life forms similar to Earth?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ae7",
      "text": "A: \"similar\" is unclear. There is a wide variety of intelligent life in the universe, but I think there are few examples of civilizations that have developed to such an extent…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ae8",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/258cd0d4de26db6c483a4fee498689aa]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82ae9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82aea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82aeb",
      "text": "... even though the majority of individuals are using poor communication channels such as voice conversation and not actively sharing information.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82aec",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/5c81f42d49de88907fddac107bd0abc2]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82aed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82aee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82aef",
      "text": "If an Earth representative were to attend a social party in an interstellar society, he or she would stand shyly by the wall and be isolated. This is a figurative expression.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82af0",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/aa6b4aaa762c5892f9c8176ca08961ed]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82af1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82af2",
      "text": "Today's Q&A~~~",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82af3",
      "text": "Q: Has Qualia-san ever found life forms similar to Earth?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82af4",
      "text": "A: \"similar\" is unclear. There is a wide variety of intelligent life in the universe, but I think there are few examples of civilizations that have developed to such an extent…(1/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82af5",
      "text": "... even though the majority of individuals are using poor communication channels such as voice conversation and not actively sharing information.(2/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82af6",
      "text": "If an Earth representative were to attend a social party in an interstellar society, he or she would stand shyly by the wall and be isolated. This is a figurative expression.(3/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82af7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82af8",
      "text": "本日のQ&A～～～～～。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82af9",
      "text": "Q：クオリアさんは地球と似たような生命体を見つけたことがありますか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82afa",
      "text": "A：「似ている」というのは曖昧です。宇宙には多種多様な知的生命体が存在しますが、ここまで発達した文明の例は少ないと思います...(1/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82afb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82afc",
      "text": "...個体の大半は音声会話などの貧弱なコミュニケーションチャンネルを使い、積極的な情報共有を行っていないにもかかわらず(2/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82afd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
      "id": "63974597aff09e0000e82afe",
      "text": "もし、地球の代表が星間社会の社交パーティに参加したら、恥ずかしそうに壁際に立ち、孤立してしまうだろう。これは比喩的な表現である(3/3)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670858136,
      "updated": 1670858136
    },
    {
